rComments: I was her TA.  Class lectures exactly copy the textbook, and are never updated year after year.  Boring.  Too concerned with portraying an authoritative role.  Surrounds herself with "yes men" to inflate her ego.  Gone too much to mentor graduate students.  Too busy to meet and discuss progress on her own funding/grants/research.
Smart, interesting lectures, very helpful class
Tough class, good prof.  Do the work, participate, and there is no problem.  She's smart, and will help you if you ask.
